UPDATE `quest_offer_reward` SET `Emote1`=1, `VerifiedBuild`=59346 WHERE `ID`=10749; -- Baron Sablemane's Poison
UPDATE `quest_offer_reward` SET `Emote1`=1, `RewardText`='Very well.  A simple, if mundane, task has been completed. Now, hand me the glands and I will do the difficult part.', `VerifiedBuild`=59346 WHERE `ID`=10715; -- Into the Churning Gulch
UPDATE `quest_offer_reward` SET `Emote1`=2, `RewardText`='Hello, $r. I am Baron Sablemane. A friend of Rexxar\'s is a friend of mine.', `VerifiedBuild`=59346 WHERE `ID`=10783; -- Baron Sablemane
UPDATE `quest_offer_reward` SET `Emote1`=1, `RewardText`='<Spirit perches upon Rexxar\'s shoulder while Rexxar listens intently.>$b$bSo it is the sons of Gruul that are behind the ogres\' actions. They command the Bloodmaul ogres to destroy the Mok\'Nathal to gain their favor.', `VerifiedBuild`=59346 WHERE `ID`=10714; -- On Spirit's Wings
UPDATE `quest_offer_reward` SET `Emote1`=1, `Emote2`=1, `RewardText`='So my father does live. I did not expect him to forgive - that was never his way. But I had hoped that the years had dulled the anger he must have felt at my departure.$b$bThirty years ago, I left the Mok\'Nathal to follow the Horde to Azeroth. Leoroxx was staunchly against it, but then, he never gave me any reason to stay. Still, I had hoped for a better welcome than this.$b$bHe wanted a Mok\'Nathal for a son and he has one now, even if he will not know it.$b$bI must open his eyes.', `VerifiedBuild`=59346 WHERE `ID`=10709; -- Reunion
UPDATE `quest_offer_reward` SET `Emote1`=1, `VerifiedBuild`=59346 WHERE `ID`=10614; -- Whispers on the Wind
UPDATE `quest_offer_reward` SET `RewardText`='Thank you, $N.$B$BWhile we\'ll see to it that the wildlife will replenish itself in quick order, regrowing the trees, especially in a natural fashion, is a much more time-intensive process.', `VerifiedBuild`=59346 WHERE `ID`=10713; -- ...and a Time for Action
UPDATE `quest_offer_reward` SET `RewardText`='That mask you hold in your hands is a Felsworn gas mask and by the appearance, it\'s not damaged. The trouble we can cause Forge Camp: Anger is boundless. Are you interested in helping us out, $N?', `VerifiedBuild`=59346 WHERE `ID`=10812; -- Mystery Mask
UPDATE `quest_offer_reward` SET `Emote1`=1, `Emote2`=1, `Emote3`=2, `EmoteDelay2`=1000, `EmoteDelay3`=1000, `RewardText`='Now that you have strengthened the wolves, and the Jagged Ridge\'s defenses, perhaps we can refocus our attentions on more deadly matters, such as the ogres?$B$BYou have done a good job in aiding us here.  We could use the help of someone capable, such as yourself, should you decide to stay.$B$BWhatever you do, you have earned my respect and appreciation.', `VerifiedBuild`=59346 WHERE `ID`=10488; -- Protecting Our Own
UPDATE `quest_offer_reward` SET `Emote1`=1, `Emote2`=1, `Emote3`=1, `EmoteDelay2`=1000, `EmoteDelay3`=1000, `RewardText`='Your actions against both the Bladespire and the Bloodmaul ogre clans have gone a long way to securing Thunderlord Stronghold\'s future.  We will not suffer those that would get in the way of our destiny here.$B$BAs you have done good work in destroying these ogres, I intend to reward you with the appreciation of the Horde.', `VerifiedBuild`=59346 WHERE `ID`=10505; -- The Bloodmaul Ogres
UPDATE `quest_offer_reward` SET `Emote1`=5, `Emote2`=1, `Emote3`=1, `EmoteDelay2`=1000, `EmoteDelay3`=1000, `RewardText`='Stronglimb Deeproot\'s Trunk!  Did you chop him down by yourself?$B$BI bet you did.  You know, Rexxar and I are looking for a young, strong $c, such as yourself, to help out around here, especially with the problems we continually have with the ogres.  Make sure that you follow-up with me on that possibility.$B$BWell that trunk\'s definitely proof, which means you\'re here to collect the bounty and not to listen to me talk.  Go ahead, take your pick.', `VerifiedBuild`=59346 WHERE `ID`=10489; -- Felling an Ancient Tree
UPDATE `quest_offer_reward` SET `Emote1`=6, `Emote2`=5, `EmoteDelay2`=1000, `VerifiedBuild`=59346 WHERE `ID`=10718; -- The Spirits Have Voices
UPDATE `quest_offer_reward` SET `Emote1`=1, `Emote2`=1, `EmoteDelay2`=1000, `VerifiedBuild`=59346 WHERE `ID`=10526; -- The Thunderspike
UPDATE `quest_offer_reward` SET `Emote1`=1, `Emote2`=1, `EmoteDelay2`=1000, `VerifiedBuild`=59346 WHERE `ID`=10487; -- Dust from the Drakes
UPDATE `quest_offer_reward` SET `RewardText`='Hahaha, revenge is sweet!$B$BBut, T\'chali can see you be interested in moving on now that you help him get his revenge.  I hear you, mon... life is for the living.$B$BTell you what, T\'chali got lots of goodies still left here in his grave.  You pick the one you like best!', `VerifiedBuild`=59346 WHERE `ID`=10544; -- A Curse Upon Both of Your Clans!
UPDATE `quest_offer_reward` SET `RewardText`='T\'chali is pleased that Korgaah and Grimnok Battleborn are pushing up daisies just like him.$B$BBut T\'chali\'s thirst for revenge is not quenched.  There\'s one more thing that you must do!', `VerifiedBuild`=59346 WHERE `ID`=10543; -- Grimnok and Korgaah, I Am For You!
UPDATE `quest_offer_reward` SET `RewardText`='That\'s good news!  That brew is gonna come in handy with what T\'chali is gonna ask you to do next.', `VerifiedBuild`=59346 WHERE `ID`=10545; -- Bladespire Kegger
UPDATE `quest_offer_reward` SET `RewardText`='Yes, that is what T\'chali is talking about!  Though me not sure what those ogres put in there; that not T\'chali\'s brand of tobacco that me smell in the hookah.$B$BNo matter, T\'chali is happy.  Happy enough, in fact, to ask you to do something else.', `VerifiedBuild`=59346 WHERE `ID`=10542; -- They Stole Me Hookah and Me Brews!
UPDATE `quest_offer_reward` SET `Emote1`=6, `Emote2`=25, `EmoteDelay2`=1000, `VerifiedBuild`=59346 WHERE `ID`=10525; -- Vision Guide
UPDATE `quest_offer_reward` SET `Emote1`=1, `Emote2`=1, `EmoteDelay2`=1000, `VerifiedBuild`=59346 WHERE `ID`=10524; -- Thunderlord Clan Artifacts
UPDATE `quest_offer_reward` SET `Emote1`=1, `Emote2`=1, `EmoteDelay2`=1000, `VerifiedBuild`=59346 WHERE `ID`=10503; -- The Bladespire Threat
UPDATE `quest_offer_reward` SET `Emote1`=6, `Emote2`=1, `EmoteDelay2`=1000, `RewardText`='That didn\'t take as long as I thought it would.  Are you sure that you dealt with as many as was necessary?$B$BVery well, there\'s something else that I want you to help us with.  Something far more important.', `VerifiedBuild`=59346 WHERE `ID`=10486; -- The Encroaching Wilderness
UPDATE `quest_offer_reward` SET `Emote1`=396, `Emote2`=396, `RewardText`='Good work, $c. That tunnel is our lifeline to the swamp.', `VerifiedBuild`=59346 WHERE `ID`=10928; -- Killing the Crawlers
UPDATE `quest_offer_reward` SET `Emote1`=1, `Emote2`=1, `Emote3`=1, `RewardText`='Denjai seeks help?  I\'d send him reinforcements, but we\'re spread thin here as it is.  We\'ve got trouble of our own with the ogres up here.$B$BWhen I can, I\'ll give him what information we have on the local ogre tribes and their tactics.  Perhaps if he can survive long enough, we\'ll be able to launch a two-pronged assault on the vile scum.', `VerifiedBuild`=59346 WHERE `ID`=9795; -- The Ogre Threat
UPDATE `quest_offer_reward` SET `Emote1`=66, `RewardText`='The battle was hard and you fought well, $n. I am honored to have stood by your side in the battle against Goc. I am thankful beyond words.$b$bThe Mok\'Nathal should know of these great defeats, but I am not ready to face them yet. I know my father\'s mind, and I know my heart. There is still much I can learn and do to become stronger, to show to him that I am his true son.', `VerifiedBuild`=59346 WHERE `ID`=10742; -- Showdown
UPDATE `quest_offer_reward` SET `RewardText`='Now we can breathe more easily knowing that the leader of our enemy has been dealt with.  Not only that, but you\'ve saved the entire mountain range from their depredations.$B$BWhatever their ultimate goals, you\'ve foiled them!$B$BYou have our gratitude, $N.  Please accept this token of our esteem, as well as our unending hospitality.', `VerifiedBuild`=59346 WHERE `ID`=10748; -- Maxnar Must Die!
UPDATE `quest_offer_reward` SET `Emote1`=1, `Emote2`=1, `RewardText`='Leokk has brought to us the head from one of the black dragons at Dragons\' End. With this, we will be able to infuriate Goc, the gronn that captured him, and lure him into battle.', `VerifiedBuild`=59346 WHERE `ID`=10724; -- Prisoner of the Bladespire
UPDATE `quest_offer_reward` SET `RewardText`='The evil is lifting from the Raven\'s Wood!  Can you feel it, $N?$B$BYou have saved us, and all of the surrounding wildlife, from certain destruction, little one!$B$BI keep stashed four magic rings amongst my boughs for such occasions as this, when a $g hero : heroine; arises to do some great deed.$B$BYou are one such $g hero : heroine;!  On behalf of all of the Raven\'s Wood, we give you thanks.', `VerifiedBuild`=59346 WHERE `ID`=10830; -- Exorcising the Trees
UPDATE `quest_offer_reward` SET `RewardText`='That is great news, great news indeed, $N. I could not have asked for a better outcome. Your service to our people is most greatly appreciated; choose one of the following heroic items.$B$BYour name will forever be remembered in our peoples\' hearts.', `VerifiedBuild`=59346 WHERE `ID`=10821; -- You're Fired!
UPDATE `quest_offer_reward` SET `Emote1`=5, `Emote2`=1, `EmoteDelay2`=1000, `RewardText`='Good that the ethereal filth and their leader are dead.  I wish a thousand plagues upon their brethren!$B$BYou are to be rewarded for your actions on behalf of all of the Mok\'Nathal, $N!  You are truly one of our heroes.$B$BLet us now release the souls of our ancestors to the cleansing fire.', `VerifiedBuild`=59346 WHERE `ID`=10867; -- There Can Be Only One Response
UPDATE `quest_offer_reward` SET `Emote1`=1, `Emote2`=11, `VerifiedBuild`=59346 WHERE `ID`=10615; -- Ruuan Weald
UPDATE `quest_offer_reward` SET `Emote1`=5, `Emote2`=6, `EmoteDelay2`=1000, `RewardText`='What you say, is it even possible?  What am I saying?  Of course it is, if the spiritcallers say so.$B$BRemember before when I said that we might need your further assistance?  It would seem that I can tell the future.', `VerifiedBuild`=59346 WHERE `ID`=10865; -- Inform Leoroxx!
UPDATE `quest_offer_reward` SET `Emote1`=5, `RewardText`='Something does not feel right.$B$BPlease, $N, hand me the totem.  I must examine those orbs!', `VerifiedBuild`=59346 WHERE `ID`=10859; -- Gather the Orbs
UPDATE `quest_offer_reward` SET `Emote1`=1, `Emote2`=6, `EmoteDelay2`=1000, `RewardText`='You have done a good thing this day, $c.  The spirits of the drakes will truly sing again now that they have been freed.  And the residual part of their spirits that they leave behind are powerful medicine, too.$B$BI wonder, are you up for a journey to the north?  There is something that I am curious about concerning the activities of the ethereal.$B$BI sense a great deal of pain coming from their direction.', `VerifiedBuild`=59346 WHERE `ID`=10853; -- Spirit Calling
UPDATE `quest_offer_reward` SET `Emote1`=6, `Emote2`=1, `Emote3`=1, `EmoteDelay2`=1000, `EmoteDelay3`=1000, `RewardText`='No?  You slew Dreadwing?  Perhaps I was wrong about you, $c.$B$BPerhaps.$B$BStill, you have slain the chiefs of the three greatest threats that we face.  That is something to be proud of.$B$BI offer you a token of my appreciation, but don\'t let it go to your head.  You still do not fully understand what it is to be Mok\'Nathal, and we may still have need to call upon your skills.', `VerifiedBuild`=59346 WHERE `ID`=10845; -- Slay the Brood Mother
UPDATE `quest_offer_reward` SET `Emote1`=1, `Emote2`=1, `EmoteDelay2`=1000, `VerifiedBuild`=59346 WHERE `ID`=10860; -- Mok'Nathal Treats
UPDATE `quest_offer_reward` SET `Emote1`=1, `Emote2`=1, `EmoteDelay1`=1000, `EmoteDelay2`=1000, `VerifiedBuild`=59346 WHERE `ID`=10843; -- Since Time Forgotten...
UPDATE `quest_offer_reward` SET `Emote1`=1, `VerifiedBuild`=59346 WHERE `ID`=10851; -- The Totems of My Enemy
UPDATE `quest_offer_reward` SET `Emote1`=1, `Emote2`=274, `Emote3`=1, `EmoteDelay2`=1000, `EmoteDelay3`=1000, `VerifiedBuild`=59346 WHERE `ID`=10846; -- Understanding the Mok'Nathal
UPDATE `quest_offer_reward` SET `Emote1`=1, `RewardText`='This information will be very helpful, $n. I will further refine that design and see if we can\'t expand its utility.', `VerifiedBuild`=59346 WHERE `ID`=10566; -- Trial and Error
UPDATE `quest_offer_reward` SET `Emote1`=2, `RewardText`='Good quality cocoons, these. I can see you\'ve gotten the hang of harvesting them.$b$bWe have experimented with trying to raise our own silkwing larva, but unfortunately the small ones do not produce enough silk to be of use to us.', `VerifiedBuild`=59346 WHERE `ID`=10617; -- Silkwing Cocoons
UPDATE `quest_offer_reward` SET `Emote1`=2, `RewardText`='Thank you, $n. We will use these sooner than you might think.', `VerifiedBuild`=59346 WHERE `ID`=10618; -- The Softest Wings
UPDATE `quest_offer_reward` SET `Emote1`=1, `Emote2`=11, `EmoteDelay1`=1000, `EmoteDelay2`=1000, `RewardText`='<Tor\'chunk grins at the story that you tell him about your adventures at Boulder\'mok.>$B$BAh, I wish that I could have been there with you.  Let me tell you something, $N: never accept any duty that keeps you from the glory of battle!$B$BHah!  After all of the ogre killing that you\'ve done, are there any still left in these mountains for me?!', `VerifiedBuild`=59346 WHERE `ID`=10786; -- Slaughter at Boulder'mok
UPDATE `quest_offer_reward` SET `Emote1`=1, `Emote2`=1, `RewardText`='The ogres of Bloodmaul and their master, Gorgrom, will trouble the Mok\'Nathal no longer.$b$bHowever, I worry about the effect our actions will have on the other gronn. I believe we must end this fight once and for all.', `VerifiedBuild`=59346 WHERE `ID`=10723; -- Gorgrom the Dragon-Eater
UPDATE `quest_offer_reward` SET `Emote1`=6, `Emote2`=5, `EmoteDelay2`=1000, `VerifiedBuild`=59346 WHERE `ID`=10785; -- It's a Trap!
UPDATE `quest_offer_reward` SET `Emote1`=1, `EmoteDelay1`=1000, `VerifiedBuild`=59346 WHERE `ID`=10721; -- A Boaring Time for Grulloc
UPDATE `quest_offer_reward` SET `RewardText`='<Chu\'a\'lor nods his heads at you in satisfaction at your accomplishment.>$B$BYou have a quick mind, $N.  It took us much longer to successfully make use of the relic.$B$BNow that you know how, you can do so as much as you care to.  Just remember that they require an apexis shard to power them.', `VerifiedBuild`=59346 WHERE `ID`=11058; -- An Apexis Relic
UPDATE `quest_offer_reward` SET `RewardText`='<Chu\'a\'lor\'s left head begins to speak.>$B$BThese will do fine.$B$BRemember, $N, the value of the shard is not in what it can purchase for you.  It is not even in what it can potentially do for you when properly forged, though there is some debate over that.$B$B<His right head finishes,...>$B$BThe true value is in the journey to attain the shard.', `VerifiedBuild`=59346 WHERE `ID`=11025; -- The Crystals
UPDATE `quest_offer_reward` SET `RewardText`='Mog\'dorg sent a message ahead, saying that I should expect you.  I am glad that you came.$B$BWith the Sons of Gruul destroyed, it is only a matter of time - a short amount at that - before the various inhabitants of this mountain terrace, and the one to the north, decide to prey upon our ogre brothers down below.$B$BI trust that you will help us to prevent that, $N.', `VerifiedBuild`=59346 WHERE `ID`=11009; -- Ogre Heaven
UPDATE `quest_offer_reward` SET `RewardText`='It is over then.  You have freed us from the shackles of our enslavement to the Sons of Gruul.  You have given the Bloodmaul Clan a reprieve from certain extinction.$B$BWords cannot describe the extent of the debt that ALL of the ogres of the Blade\'s Edge Mountains, Bloodmaul and Bladespire alike, owe you, $N.$B$BLook down, even now the ogres gather to pay you tribute.  Let Gruul and his puppet, the old king, Maulgar, cower within their lair.  Go to the ogres below as our new $g king : queen;!', `VerifiedBuild`=59346 WHERE `ID`=11000; -- Into the Soulgrinder
UPDATE `quest_offer_reward` SET `RewardText`='What a relief that Slaag is gone.  No longer will we be threatened by the looming specter of his return!$B$BIf you do not mind, I will take the standard as a symbol of hope for all of the ogres of the mountains.$B$BThank you, $N.', `VerifiedBuild`=59346 WHERE `ID`=10997; -- Even Gronn Have Standards
UPDATE `quest_offer_reward` SET `EmoteDelay2`=4000, `VerifiedBuild`=59346 WHERE `ID`=10136; -- Cruel's Intentions
UPDATE `quest_offer_reward` SET `Emote1`=66, `VerifiedBuild`=59346 WHERE `ID`=10876; -- The Foot of the Citadel
UPDATE `quest_offer_reward` SET `Emote1`=1, `Emote2`=5, `Emote3`=1, `RewardText`='It is good to hear of all your moves against the fel orcs, $N.  The apothecaries have spent much time and resources studying the cause of their corruption, and although such information is invaluable... my orc blood burns to strike a severe blow against these betrayers!$B$BListen close, and I will explain my task...', `VerifiedBuild`=59346 WHERE `ID`=10875; -- Report to Nazgrel
UPDATE `quest_offer_reward` SET `Emote1`=1, `VerifiedBuild`=59346 WHERE `ID`=10838; -- The Demoniac Scryer
UPDATE `quest_offer_reward` SET `Emote1`=11, `Emote2`=11, `EmoteDelay1`=1000, `EmoteDelay2`=4000, `RewardText`='You have saved my life\'s work $N.  $B$BThey called me insane, they laughed at me, they thought I was mad for my obsession with the Void Ridge and Warp Fields.  Now with this soul shard I can unlock the secrets of the voidwalkers.  I will command the power of the abyss.  ', `VerifiedBuild`=59346 WHERE `ID`=10295; -- From the Abyss
UPDATE `quest_offer_reward` SET `Emote1`=1, `RewardText`='Ah, yes.  Just as some who lost a hand or a leg in battle will oftentimes feel their severed limb, I wonder if Grillok still clutched at his lost eye in his dark, dark dreams...$B$BI too will dream on this, and if fortune is with us then perhaps I will learn what drew Grillok and the Bleeding Hollow orcs to succumb to demons.', `VerifiedBuild`=59346 WHERE `ID`=10834; -- Grillok "Darkeye"
UPDATE `quest_offer_reward` SET `RewardText`='You\'re a brave $c, $N.  That savage beast took many of my best hunters\' lives.$B$BTake this reward, you\'ve earned it.', `VerifiedBuild`=59346 WHERE `ID`=9466; -- Wanted: Blacktalon the Savage
UPDATE `quest_offer_reward` SET `RewardText`='Goliathon?  Pathaleon the Calculator?$B$BKAEL\'THAS!?$B$BPrince Kael\'thas has a hand in this?$B$B<The earthbinder fumes.>$B$BIt is insanity what he has done!  Dropping giant crystals from the sky and decimating the land can only be the work of a madman!$B$BI can assure you, the Cenarion Expedition will counter any further attempts by their forces to do this ever again.$B$BWe owe you a great debt, $N.', `VerifiedBuild`=59346 WHERE `ID`=10351; -- Natural Remedies
UPDATE `quest_offer_reward` SET `RewardText`='It is true, $N.  I was once Naladu the Keeper of Earth.$B$BIt was I who betrayed the other Dreghood elders in exchange for empty promises of power.  You can despise me now if you wish to.  What matters is that my tribe is free once again and that the spirits have returned to us.$B$BI will not be joining the rest of the tribe, but I can die in peace now.  May the spirit of earth find a new servant among my brothers.', `VerifiedBuild`=59346 WHERE `ID`=10369; -- Arzeth's Demise
UPDATE `quest_offer_reward` SET `RewardText`='I can feel it, $N!   The spirits are returning to us.', `VerifiedBuild`=59346 WHERE `ID`=10368; -- The Dreghood Elders
UPDATE `quest_offer_reward` SET `RewardText`='I thank you, $N.  My people will soon be free thanks to you.', `VerifiedBuild`=59346 WHERE `ID`=10367; -- A Traitor Among Us
UPDATE `quest_offer_reward` SET `RewardText`='<Thiah Redmane\'s eyes widen as you describe the results of the experiment.>$B$BBut, how could that happen? I\'m certain I prepared the antidote correctly!$B$BI\'ve seen it work with spider and snake venoms, so why would it backfire here? Perhaps that\'s one of Outland\'s many peculiarities, $N. I\'d best pass this information along to my comrades.', `VerifiedBuild`=59346 WHERE `ID`=10255; -- Testing the Antidote
UPDATE `quest_offer_reward` SET `RewardText`='Well done, $N. These blood samples will prove helpful in my research and in the Expedition\'s wider studies of Outland\'s creatures.$B$BIf I could isolate what causes these creatures to change continuously, perhaps I could concoct an antidote.', `VerifiedBuild`=59346 WHERE `ID`=9372; -- Demonic Contamination
UPDATE `quest_offer_reward` SET `EmoteDelay2`=1000, `VerifiedBuild`=59346 WHERE `ID`=10442; -- Helping the Cenarion Post
UPDATE `quest_offer_reward` SET `Emote1`=1, `VerifiedBuild`=59346 WHERE `ID`=9376; -- A Pilgrim's Plight
UPDATE `quest_offer_reward` SET `Emote1`=1, `RewardText`='<Taleris shouts to several of the blood elves at the outpost.>$B$BGet her inside and see to her wounds!$B$B<Taleris turns back to you.>$B$BShe\'s fortunate that you found her when you did, $c. I don\'t think she\'d have lasted much longer out there.$B$BCan you make out what she was saying? ', `VerifiedBuild`=59346 WHERE `ID`=9375; -- The Road to Falcon Watch
UPDATE `quest_offer_reward` SET `Emote1`=5, `Emote2`=4, `EmoteDelay1`=500, `EmoteDelay2`=1000, `VerifiedBuild`=59346 WHERE `ID`=9406; -- The Mag'har
UPDATE `quest_offer_reward` SET `RewardText`='Good job, $N.  That should teach the rock flayers to stay far away from us.', `VerifiedBuild`=59346 WHERE `ID`=9340; -- The Great Fissure
UPDATE `quest_offer_reward` SET `Emote1`=1, `RewardText`='These should do the job. I was concerned that the rangers might be short on arrows for a while, but that\'s one less thing I have to worry about. Thank you for your help, $c.', `VerifiedBuild`=59346 WHERE `ID`=9381; -- Trueflight Arrows
UPDATE `quest_offer_reward` SET `RewardText`='Welcome to Falcon Watch, $r.  All our Horde allies are welcome here, especially those recommended by Martik.', `VerifiedBuild`=59346 WHERE `ID`=9498; -- Falcon Watch
UPDATE `quest_offer_reward` SET `EmoteDelay1`=4000, `VerifiedBuild`=59346 WHERE `ID`=10258; -- Honor the Fallen
UPDATE `quest_offer_reward` SET `Emote1`=5, `RewardText`='Hah!  I could see the smoke and flames of Zeth\'Gor from here!  May the Bleeding Hollow fiends burn to ash and drift far from the sight of any true orc!$B$BThank you, $N.  You helped burn away an afront to every orc\'s spirit.', `VerifiedBuild`=59346 WHERE `ID`=10792; -- Zeth'Gor Must Burn!
UPDATE `quest_offer_reward` SET `Emote1`=11, `EmoteDelay1`=4000, `RewardText`='Excellent, the warp rift generator is almost complete.  There is only one final ingredient we require.  Soon we shall be able to open up a warp rift to the deepest parts of the abyss.  $B$BWho knows what strange creature may come through?  Think of it $N, the power such knowledge will bring is limitless.  ', `VerifiedBuild`=59346 WHERE `ID`=10294; -- Void Ridge
UPDATE `quest_offer_reward` SET `Emote1`=273, `RewardText`='I am indebted to you, $n.  You have again braved Zeth\'Gor and held its darkness close to your heart.  I will study the eye and perhaps pierce the secrets of its master, Grillok.$B$BLet us hope that he can no longer use its magic!', `VerifiedBuild`=59346 WHERE `ID`=10813; -- The Eyes of Grillok
UPDATE `quest_offer_reward` SET `EmoteDelay1`=2000, `VerifiedBuild`=59346 WHERE `ID`=10278; -- The Warp Rifts
UPDATE `quest_offer_reward` SET `Emote1`=1, `RewardText`='Well done, $N.  Your soul is burdened with many deaths... and the Demonaic Scryer will now perform its duties for you.$B$BLet us hope you are ready for the coming trial...', `VerifiedBuild`=59346 WHERE `ID`=10864; -- A Burden of Souls
UPDATE `quest_offer_reward` SET `Emote1`=113, `EmoteDelay1`=6000, `RewardText`='Praise the ancients, you\'ve done it, $N! The Legion has suffered a terrible defeat - and Thrallmar is safe once again. Ah, if I had but a hundred warriors with your heart and cunning, this broken land would be tamed already! I salute you.  $B$B<Nazgrel salutes you crisply>\n', `VerifiedBuild`=59346 WHERE `ID`=10392; -- Doorway to the Abyss
UPDATE `quest_offer_reward` SET `Emote1`=4, `EmoteDelay1`=4000, `VerifiedBuild`=59346 WHERE `ID`=10390; -- Forge Camp: Mageddon
UPDATE `quest_offer_reward` SET `Emote1`=1, `RewardText`='Ah, a report from Albreck?  Very good.  The Royal Apothecary Society works feverishly to determine how the orcs of Hellfire Peninsula became fel orcs.  Their betrayal is unforgivable... and we must ensure that our orc friends are forever safe from future corruption.', `VerifiedBuild`=59346 WHERE `ID`=10835; -- Apothecary Antonivich
