UPDATE `quest_offer_reward` SET `RewardText`='Let\'s take a closer look at these weapons, $N.  Hmmm... this is rather unsettling.', `VerifiedBuild`=59346 WHERE `ID`=10687; -- Karabor Training Grounds
UPDATE `quest_offer_reward` SET `RewardText`='<Archmage Vargoth\'s image examines you as you convey Ravandwyr\'s message.>$B$BRavandwyr has everything a master can expect of his apprentice. When I gave him the staff and told him to flee, I hoped that he would use it to find help and free me once Kael\'thas\'s forces withdrew from the tower. Since then, I have learned a great deal about the nature of the curse.$B$BIt can be broken, $N, but it will require your help.', `VerifiedBuild`=59346 WHERE `ID`=10174; -- Curse of the Violet Tower
UPDATE `quest_offer_reward` SET `RewardText`='You\'re one reliable $g fellow : lass;, $N.  If there\'s one thing I like more than killing Kael\'s lapdogs, it is having someone else do it for me.$B$BLess blood on my clothes that way.', `VerifiedBuild`=59346 WHERE `ID`=10193; -- High Value Targets
UPDATE `quest_offer_reward` SET `RewardText`='I am impressed, $N, though I should expect nothing less of the $g hero : heroine; who returned the ata\'mal crystal to us.$B$BGive over the two shards and I will see to it that they are combined into their final form.  Then you will have access to the Arcatraz.', `VerifiedBuild`=59346 WHERE `ID`=10704; -- How to Break Into the Arcatraz
UPDATE `quest_offer_reward` SET `RewardText`='You are an individual of formidable power, $N.  The Scryers are fortunate to count you as an ally.$B$BAs word of Kael\'s new allegiance spreads, more people will see things our way.  The fact that we can claim such a decisive victory against Kael\'thas\' new overlords puts us in a most favorable situation.$B$BI will not forget your deeds.', `VerifiedBuild`=59346 WHERE `ID`=10507; -- Turning Point
UPDATE `quest_offer_reward` SET `RewardText`='You have recovered Spirit\'s Song!  It is the ata\'mal crystal that Prophet Velen left behind with his people for safekeeping before he went upon his ill-fated mission to the Exodar.$B$BOdd that he did not foresee it falling into the hands of the Burning Legion, if even for a short time.$B$BOr, perhaps he did?  It may be that he foresaw all of this, and left it there so that you would retrieve the crystal and deliver it to me here?$B$BI sense that is the truth of it.  You are a great hero of your people, $N!', `VerifiedBuild`=59346 WHERE `ID`=10280; -- Special Delivery to Shattrath City
UPDATE `quest_offer_reward` SET `RewardText`='You have no idea what this will mean for the Scryers, $N.  You will have to excuse me while I catch my breath and assess the situation.', `VerifiedBuild`=59346 WHERE `ID`=10509; -- Bound for Glory
UPDATE `quest_offer_reward` SET `RewardText`='Beyond my wildest dreams, I never thought that you would be able to retrieve the crystal!$B$BAnd then to actually give it to me!  Do you have any idea how powerful it is?$B$BYour selflessness is inspirational and beyond reproach, $N!  You have given me much to think about.', `VerifiedBuild`=59346 WHERE `ID`=10276; -- Full Triangle
UPDATE `quest_offer_reward` SET `RewardText`='$N!  Or, should I say Junior Technician 1st Grade $N?!  Oh hell, who am I kidding?  Skipping a grade isn\'t a good enough reward for what you\'ve done.  I\'m going to make you my first officer!$B$BYou\'ve saved all of us, and more importantly the X-52 Nether-Rocket!  I could just kiss you... but I won\'t.$B$BInstead, please let me present you with the gratitude of Area 52.  Take your pick!', `VerifiedBuild`=59346 WHERE `ID`=10249; -- Back to the Chief!
UPDATE `quest_offer_reward` SET `RewardText`='You do not cease to amaze me, $N!  Good thing you\'re on our side.', `VerifiedBuild`=59346 WHERE `ID`=10508; -- A Gift for Voren'thal
UPDATE `quest_offer_reward` SET `RewardText`='<You describe the results of your scrying.>$B$BCommander Sarannis, you say? Hmm...$B$BShe\'s one of Kael\'thas\'s advisors, but certainly not a mage. I remember her from the attack on Kirin\'Var Village. I think your impressions are correct, $N. She\'s not maintaining the curse personally, but she holds the key to it.', `VerifiedBuild`=59346 WHERE `ID`=10256; -- Finding the Keymaster
UPDATE `quest_offer_reward` SET `RewardText`='The defeat of Naberius is a great achievement, $N. I can\'t help thinking that we might have had a chance against Kael\'thas\'s forces if the apprentice\'s loyalties had been in the right place that day.', `VerifiedBuild`=59346 WHERE `ID`=10320; -- Destroy Naberius!
UPDATE `quest_offer_reward` SET `RewardText`='Well done, $N. Well done indeed. The nether dragonkin will not accept a blue dragon among them at first, but with time and the firm demonstration of my authority, they will come around. Scattered, isolated, and without a definitive leader, we must be vigilant in preventing them from falling under the sway of a malevolent power, keeping them in check all the while.', `VerifiedBuild`=59346 WHERE `ID`=10274; -- Securing the Celestial Ridge
UPDATE `quest_offer_reward` SET `RewardText`='Stand back, $N. This could very well be an Ethereum trap.', `VerifiedBuild`=59346 WHERE `ID`=10970; -- A Mission of Mercy
UPDATE `quest_offer_reward` SET `RewardText`='It has been a thousand years, maybe more, since Salhadaar began his crusade to exterminate all that would stand in his way. I can hardly believe that this is the last we\'ll see of him... You have done all of us a great service, $N, and for that you will be rewarded.', `VerifiedBuild`=59346 WHERE `ID`=10408; -- Nexus-King Salhadaar
UPDATE `quest_offer_reward` SET `RewardText`='This is big, $N.  Very big!$B$BVoren\'thal is going to want to hear about this as soon as possible.', `VerifiedBuild`=59346 WHERE `ID`=10432; -- Damning Evidence
UPDATE `quest_offer_reward` SET `RewardText`='Thanks to you, $N, I\'ll breathe a little easier.  Figure of speech, of course!$B$BI suppose you\'ll want some form of reward now.', `VerifiedBuild`=59346 WHERE `ID`=10857; -- Teleport This!
UPDATE `quest_offer_reward` SET `RewardText`='These will work quite nicely, $N. Thank you for agreeing to help us.$B$BBefore we can continue, however, there is something else we\'ll need to address.', `VerifiedBuild`=59346 WHERE `ID`=10272; -- A Promising Start
UPDATE `quest_offer_reward` SET `RewardText`='You saved my wrappings, $N. The Protectorate will know of what you\'ve done on this day, friend.', `VerifiedBuild`=59346 WHERE `ID`=10345; -- The Flesh Lies...
UPDATE `quest_offer_reward` SET `RewardText`='Thank you, $N. Tyralius suffered massive injuries but we think he\'s going to make it.$B$BHe mentioned fields of prisons, much like the one you rescued him from. Prisons full of creatures from all across the universe!$B$BWe\'ll be in touch should a need arise to crack those open. The Consortium has already expressed some interest in sending some teams out and is working on some technology to break through the Ethereum\'s locks.\n', `VerifiedBuild`=59346 WHERE `ID`=10422; -- Captain Tyralius
UPDATE `quest_offer_reward` SET `RewardText`='Nice work, $N.  Keep it up and I\'ll put in a good word with the Nexus-Prince.', `VerifiedBuild`=59346 WHERE `ID`=10856; -- The Best Defense
UPDATE `quest_offer_reward` SET `RewardText`='This looks a little peculiar. Ghabar definitely didn\'t have Netherstorm in mind when he designed it.$B$BDon\'t look so surprised, $N. Netherstorm is tame compared to some of the environments I\'ve worked in. Nevertheless, a failing dome is always a concern.', `VerifiedBuild`=59346 WHERE `ID`=10430; -- Testing the Prototype
UPDATE `quest_offer_reward` SET `RewardText`='That is excellent news, $N.  Now that we know how to deal with these, I can have hirelings sabotage any remaining reavers.', `VerifiedBuild`=59346 WHERE `ID`=10855; -- Fel Reavers, No Thanks!
UPDATE `quest_offer_reward` SET `RewardText`='A doomguard overmaster?  That\'s odd!  What\'s the Burning Legion doing in there?$B$BSo, some of the blood elves are defecting.  We\'ll keep that in mind if we ever attempt to take the place by force.  At least there\'s some good news that has come from all of this, no?$B$BPlease, $N, take this with my deepest gratitude.', `VerifiedBuild`=59346 WHERE `ID`=10318; -- Dealing with the Overmaster
UPDATE `quest_offer_reward` SET `RewardText`='You\'ve done well, $N.  Kael\'s army will not easily recover from the blow you\'ve dealt today.', `VerifiedBuild`=59346 WHERE `ID`=10341; -- Kick Them While They're Down
UPDATE `quest_offer_reward` SET `RewardText`='That makes three manaforges you\'ve shut down, $N.  Kael\'thas must be having a real fit right about now.', `VerifiedBuild`=59346 WHERE `ID`=10338; -- Shutting Down Manaforge Duro
UPDATE `quest_offer_reward` SET `RewardText`='Well, that\'s good and bad news, now isn\'t it?  We\'ve dealt them a blow, but with the Burning Legion running free all over the Netherstorm - and getting closer to us here - well, I don\'t know how it\'s going to go.$B$BI have a feeling that we\'re going to have to change gears here for a while.  Hope you\'ll be able to help us out, $N.', `VerifiedBuild`=59346 WHERE `ID`=10232; -- In A Scrap With The Legion
UPDATE `quest_offer_reward` SET `RewardText`='Well, I for one am glad that this petty little business is behind us.  I cannot remember a time when the Consortium has had dealings with such boorish and untrustworthy beings.$B$BYou, however, seem to be very trustworthy, $N.  Perhaps you wouldn\'t mind doing me one more favor?', `VerifiedBuild`=59346 WHERE `ID`=10267; -- Rightful Repossession
UPDATE `quest_offer_reward` SET `RewardText`='You do not cease to amaze me, $N.  That was quite the feat of stealth you pulled off at Manaforge Coruu.', `VerifiedBuild`=59346 WHERE `ID`=10200; -- Return to Thalodien
UPDATE `quest_offer_reward` SET `RewardText`='You have done well, $N. Destroying the dampening field will make it much easier for me to prepare the magic that will lift the tower\'s curse at last.', `VerifiedBuild`=59346 WHERE `ID`=10176; -- Ar'kelos the Guardian
UPDATE `quest_offer_reward` SET `RewardText`='Excellent work. Keep your fingers crossed, $N. I\'m going to activate the shield.', `VerifiedBuild`=59346 WHERE `ID`=10240; -- Building a Perimeter
UPDATE `quest_offer_reward` SET `RewardText`='Excellent, $N. Now, we have most of what we\'ll need to attempt to break Kael\'thas\'s magic.$B$BAnd if the blood elves suffer from the loss of their local commander, so much the better.', `VerifiedBuild`=59346 WHERE `ID`=10301; -- Unlocking the Compendium
UPDATE `quest_offer_reward` SET `RewardText`='<Archmage Vargoth\'s image seems to inspect the compendium.>$B$BIt\'s a little worse for the wear, but considering the treatment it\'s been through, it\'s a miracle all of it survived. Safeguard it, $N. Without it, we stand little chance of being able to break the tower\'s ward.', `VerifiedBuild`=59346 WHERE `ID`=10192; -- Krasus's Compendium
UPDATE `quest_offer_reward` SET `RewardText`='Excellent work, $N. Possession of the phylactery will be the key to our victory. When you enter battle with Naberius, I will smash it, exposing him to your attacks.', `VerifiedBuild`=59346 WHERE `ID`=10319; -- Capturing the Phylactery
UPDATE `quest_offer_reward` SET `Emote1`=1, `Emote2`=1, `Emote3`=1, `VerifiedBuild`=59346 WHERE `ID`=10306; -- Conjurer Luminrath
UPDATE `quest_offer_reward` SET `RewardText`='You\'ve done well, $N. I can no longer sense any restlessness in Dathric\'s spirit. I would give much for the opportunity to speak to him one more time, but it is enough that he is finally at rest.', `VerifiedBuild`=59346 WHERE `ID`=10182; -- Battle-Mage Dathric
UPDATE `quest_offer_reward` SET `RewardText`='Bessy, is that you?$B$B<The farmer turns to you.>$B$BThank you for bringing back my Bessy, $N. I couldn\'t live without her!', `VerifiedBuild`=59346 WHERE `ID`=10337; -- When the Cows Come Home
UPDATE `quest_offer_reward` SET `RewardText`='It\'s a relief to hear that scum is finally dealt with.  You do good work, $N... may I be so forward as to call you by your name?$B$BIf you\'re willing, I have another task that needs doing.  One that is very important and someone of your obvious skill should be able to handle with ease.', `VerifiedBuild`=59346 WHERE `ID`=10205; -- Warp-Raider Nesaad
UPDATE `quest_offer_reward` SET `Emote1`=1, `Emote2`=1, `Emote3`=1, `VerifiedBuild`=59346 WHERE `ID`=10633; -- Teron Gorefiend - Lore and Legend
UPDATE `quest_offer_reward` SET `RewardText`='Only air remains, $N.', `VerifiedBuild`=59346 WHERE `ID`=10480; -- Enraged Spirits of Water
UPDATE `quest_offer_reward` SET `Emote1`=1, `Emote2`=1, `VerifiedBuild`=59346 WHERE `ID`=10761; -- Find the Deserter
UPDATE `quest_offer_reward` SET `Emote1`=1, `Emote2`=1, `RewardText`='<Grokom accepts the weapon fragment from you.>$B$BI haven\'t seen this in years. Not only is it made from a rare ore, but it\'s not about to be used in an ordinary weapon, $N.$B$BThese runes imbue the blade with the power to obliterate demons. This shows how much the Legion hates Illidan, if they\'re willing to arm their own troops with demon-destroying weapons. We could use this to our advantage.', `VerifiedBuild`=59346 WHERE `ID`=10623; -- Illidari-Bane Shard
