UPDATE `quest_offer_reward` SET `Emote1`=1, `Emote2`=1, `Emote3`=1, `RewardText`='Gorefiend? T... Teron Gorefiend? But... How?$B$BHow could Gorefiend be here? This is impossible!$B$BThe legend of Teron Gorefiend is one that causes even the Forsaken to tremble in fear. By all accounts, Gorefiend was a warlock of Gul\'dan - extremely powerful in his own right. When Gorefiend was slain by Orgrim Doomhammer, Gul\'dan took the soul of the fallen warlock and placed it inside the broken shell of a slain knight of Stormwind. And so was born the first death knight of the Horde.', `VerifiedBuild`=59346 WHERE `ID`=10625; -- Spectrecles
